channel.title: Old-Age - Ultimate F2P Server
channel.description:
[CENTER]Well i've been working on this for about a week and spent about 30 minutes overall on it, Because i have been busy with school and collage, and my social life.
So here it goes,
I decided to make a F2P Server, Because their fun to make and fun to play. Basically also. If you love f2p on Runescape, But the training is too slow. You can join us and still become a high level but faster.
Their will be time to time switches from Members minigames Converted to our F2P World.
Now what im going to show you what i've added in the past hour. [B] Added:[/B] -13 Dialogues. -Home Area In lumbridge. -Full F2P Autospawn. -Doors/Ladders -Removed Theiving -Removed All Members Skills. -Fixed Clan chat (Can now connect and chat) -Al-Kharid gates, With gaurds (Currently free to enter) -Full Runescape modern teleports. -45x Runescape rates, Most servers are about 200. -Started on F2P Shops. [B] Images:[/B] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o2.jpg[/img] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o3.jpg[/img] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o4.jpg[/img] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o5.jpg[/img] [img]http://i488.photobucket.com/albums/rr242/3skillzzzzz/o6.jpg[/img]
[B]Credits:[/B] Legacy/Brawler (ME). Sanity.[/CENTER]
